text: Kent Smith (1907-1985) was an American actor. Kent Smith may also refer to: *Kent Smith (politician) (born 1966), American politician in the Ohio House of Representatives *Kent Smith (producer), Australian cinematographer and film producer *Kent Warner Smith (1941–2008), American political and civil rights activist ==See also== *List of people with surname Smith *Smith (disambiguation) *Smith (surname)
